outputs.output_descr: The project will achieve: (1) Protected Area system of the Philippines has been expanded under new and diverse management regimes ( ancestral domain, local government and community management areas) to cover an additional 400,000 hectares  of Key Biodiversity Area(KBAs) and with enhanced potential for further expansion;  (2) improved conservation effectiveness through enhanced systemic, institutional and individual capacities; (3) enhanced sustainability of the terrestrial PA system.

project_descr: Expanding and Diversifying the National System of Terrestrial Protected Areas in the Philippines
project_title: Expanding & Diversifying the National System of Phil PAs
